body.p:
You might be tempted to share access to your social media account,
			for example if you want to have postings regularly,
			even while you are away.

Dealing with these attacks can be emotionally draining;
			even just reading the messages can have a far greater impact on you than you realise.
			Take breaks in the event of an attack, even if it's hard to - consider going for a walk to force yourself away.
